-Sredit ću te, Chip!

00:31:52.375 --> 00:31:55.125
Koji kurac!
Sranje, sranje, sranje!

00:31:56.875 --> 00:31:58.875
Sranje, sranje!

00:32:43.500 --> 00:32:45.500
Jebemti!

